因为 $\eta$ 是 $\xi$ 的线性函数，所以有
$$
\begin{aligned}
f_{\eta}(y) &= f_{\xi}(x(y))\left|x^{\prime}(y)\right| \\
&= \begin{cases} 1\cdot\left|\frac{1}{2}\right|, & 0 \leq \frac{y-1}{2} \leq 1 \\ 0, & \text { 其它 } \end{cases} \\
&= \begin{cases} \frac{1}{2}, & 1 \leq y \leq 3 \\ 0, & \text{其它} \end{cases}
\end{aligned}
$$

$$f_Y(y)=\begin{cases} f_X\left(\frac{y-d}{c}\right) \cdot \frac{1}{|c|}, & a \leq \frac{y-d}{c} \leq b \\ 0, & \text{其它} \end{cases}$$
当 $c>0$ 时, $f_Y(y)=\begin{cases} \frac{1}{c(b-a)}, & ca+d \leq y \leq cb+d \\ 0, & \text{其它} \end{cases}$;
当 $c<0$ 时, $f_Y(y)=\begin{cases} -\frac{1}{c(b-a)}, & cb+d \leq y \leq ca+d \\ 0, & \text{其它} \end{cases}$.

因为在 $[0,1]$ 上 $Y=X^2+1$ 是单调可导函数, 故有
$$
\begin{aligned}
f_Y(y) & =f_X(x(y))\left|x^{\prime}(y)\right| \\
& =\left\{\begin{array}{ll}
1 \cdot\left|\frac{1}{2 \sqrt{y-1}}\right|, & 0<\sqrt{y-1} \leq 1 \\
0, & \text { 其它 }
\end{array}\right. =\left\{\begin{array}{ll}
\frac{1}{2 \sqrt{y-1}}, & 1<y \leq 2 \\
0, & \text { 其它 }
\end{array} \right.
\end{aligned}
$$

故 $P\{0 \leq Y \leq 1\}=0$.
